Ghost Comps is a simple api to controls display objects UI Based like, buttons, sliders, lists, etc.
The objective is implement a minimal functional part of ui controls but, keeping a easy way to improve your UI with particular functionalities.

Current Project Site:
http://github.com/jancassio/ghostcomps/

